<p>Some states also allow for OTB sites to exist without a racetrack and take horse racing wagers. These also will typically broadcast all races they are taking wagers on live on location.</p>



<h2 id='in-person-betting'  id="boomdevs_4" class="wp-block-heading" >In-Person Betting</h2>



<p>If you are one of the lucky ones that can attend the Belmont Park on Saturday, you can place a wager at the betting window on the day of the race. Enjoy the show!</p>



